track_notes:
A straightforward route up and back via a shooters track from public road. I cycled/pushed my bike up (71 mins) and cycled down (white knuckle 24 mins). Watch out for gamekeepers from Gunnerside Estate. I was confronted and told to leave. The summit was well qualified by then. Suggest when activating you be discrete. This is open access land so you cannot be stopped getting to and from the summit much to the chagrin of the gamekeeper!  
4.25 miles up with 1270ft ascent visited solo 23/08/2008.
track_title: G/NP-014 Rogans Seat Swaledale from Dyke Heads

track_notes:
From the Campsite at Keld via Crackpot Hall and Swinner Gill - a good place to cool your feet - it was in the 80s the day I did this walk.
I spoke to the Gamekeeper for about ten minutes and he was quite friendly, maybe Phil met him on an off day.
